♪When a whale falls, thousands rise♪

185
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:41,180
♪May we, amid fields of blossoms♪

186
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:44,580
♪Look back upon the long road
we have traveled♪

187
00:11:46,060 --> 00:11:47,020
You are back.

188
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:48,900
Zhiyao.

189
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:50,940
What happened to you?

190
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:07,460
I... I'm fine.

191
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,900
Why are you still up?

192
00:12:24,660 --> 00:12:25,500
It's getting cold.

193
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:27,300
Ginger soup helps ward off the chill.

194
00:12:27,900 --> 00:12:29,500
I'll go rest after you drink it.

195
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:33,060
Eldest Young Master,

196
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:35,700
there's no need for this.

197
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:37,420
What we agreed upon

198
00:12:37,420 --> 00:12:38,940
doesn't oblige you to do any of this.

199
00:12:41,180 --> 00:12:44,100
I treat you well because I want to,

200
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:46,500
not because of our agreement.

201
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:02,140
Just as I suspected.

202
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:05,260
I'd like to see

203
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:08,780
how you try to deny it this time.

204
00:13:27,860 --> 00:13:33,740
♪The secret about you
is buried deep in my heart♪

205
00:13:34,340 --> 00:13:40,180
♪I draw near, then pull away, fearing
I might yield to this attraction♪

206
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:44,180
♪I like to think I'm keeping my cool♪

207
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:46,980
♪But my instincts
keep pulling me closer♪

208
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:53,780
♪Unwittingly,
I've fallen completely for you♪

209
00:13:53,980 --> 00:14:00,140
♪Can the sacrifices of this life
measure the depth of love?♪

210
00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:06,740
♪It's too late to summon the courage
to hold you once more♪

211
00:14:07,420 --> 00:14:10,540
♪Having witnessed
all the world's splendor♪

212
00:14:10,540 --> 00:14:13,300
♪I've felt joy and sorrow
for one soul alone♪

213
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:19,540
♪For our kindred souls,
all I can give is this humble heart♪

214
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:23,380
♪If I encounter you in this life♪

215
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:26,100
♪Fate is already fulfilled♪

216
00:14:26,460 --> 00:14:32,520
♪Let this chapter become a memory,
breaking free from destiny♪

217
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:39,300
♪In the next life,
may the course of time lead me to you♪

218
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:45,900
♪With a sincere heart,
I shall carry our love forward♪
